# CODEOWNERS — solo repo today, scaffolded for team expansion.
#
# Pattern below sets @jra2s394 as default on every PR (current state) AND
# also pins ownership of the high-blast-radius surfaces. When a teammate
# joins, you only need to (a) add their handle to the catch-all line and
# (b) leave the sensitive-path lines pointing at you — that guarantees the
# surfaces below always require maintainer review even when other teammates
# can self-approve everything else.

# Default owner — applies to every file unless overridden below.
* @jra2s394

# High blast radius — settings, hooks, CI, security policy, repo-wide config.
# Changes here can silently weaken the safeguards the rest of the repo
# depends on, so they should always require the maintainer's review.
/.claude/settings.json       @jra2s394
/.claude/settings.local.json @jra2s394
/hooks/                      @jra2s394
/.github/workflows/          @jra2s394
/SECURITY.md                 @jra2s394
/.github/SECURITY.md         @jra2s394
/CLAUDE.md                   @jra2s394
/pyproject.toml              @jra2s394
/.pre-commit-config.yaml     @jra2s394
